Guided Exercise: Configure Network Policies
Goal of This Exercise
Main objectives:
1️⃣ Create NetworkPolicies
2️⃣ Restrict communication between pods
3️⃣ Allow only specific traffic
You will see the progression:
Step 1: Everything allowed
Step 2: Deny all traffic
Step 3: Allow specific traffic
Step 4: Allow router traffic
