23. Router Access
Routes require router pods.
Router namespace:
openshift-ingress
Policy file:
allow-from-openshift-ingress.yaml
Example:
spec:
  podSelector:
    matchLabels:
      deployment: hello
  ingress:
  - from:
    - namespaceSelector:
        matchLabels:
          policy-group.network.openshift.io/ingress: ""
Meaning:
Allow router pods
________________________________________
Apply:
oc create -n network-policy -f allow-from-openshift-ingress.yaml
________________________________________
Check policies:
oc get networkpolicies
Example:
deny-all
allow-specific
allow-from-openshift-ingress
________________________________________
24. Test Route Again
Command:
curl hello-network-policy.apps.ocp4.example.com
